  <brief_title>Does the National Health Insurance Card Allow us to Predict Antibiotic Resistance?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Does the National Health Insurance Card Allow us to Predict Antibiotic Resistance? Pilot Study to Guide Probabilistic Antibiotic Regimens of Community-acquired Urinary Tract Infections</official_title>
  <sponsors>
